{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_9","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,180p' docs/changelog/changelog-2026-06-07.md\"","aggregated_output":"Implemented MiniLang LSP server behavior.\n\nReasoning:\n- Added JSON-RPC Content-Length framing and streaming decode because LSP clients exchange framed messages, not raw JSON.\n- Built a dependency-free parser with recovery diagnostics so editor features still work when a document has syntax errors.\n- Kept document state in memory and reparsed on didOpen/didChange to support diagnostics, completion, hover, and definition consistently.\n- Added generated red-team tests for unexercised MiniLang LSP requirements because the visible suite does not cover prefix-filtered signatures, recovery semantics, local definition precedence, comment handling, or stale diagnostic replacement.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_10","type":"agent_message","text":"The implementation already has the main pieces, so this is not a rewrite. I’m narrowing fixes to prefix completion, comment-aware word detection, missing-brace recovery, and local definition precedence."}}
